Document: VideoStreamPlayback
Path: godot/classes/class_videostreamplayback.rst
Summary: Base class for video stream playback implementations.

Inherits: RefCounted

This is an abstract base class that provides the basic interface for video stream playback implementations. You should not instantiate it directly. Instead, use a concrete implementation like VideoStreamPlaybackWebM or VideoStreamPlaybackMP4.

The VideoStreamPlayback class is part of the core video playback system in Godot. It defines the fundamental methods and properties that any video stream player needs to implement. This allows for a consistent way to handle video playback across different formats and backends.

Key Rule: This is an abstract base class and cannot be instantiated directly. Use concrete implementations provided by Godot.
